Vladimir Nabokov





TO: FRANCIS BROWN1

CC, 1 p.





Res.: 802 East Seneca Street

Ithaca, N.Y.

April 19, 1951

Dear Mr. Brown,

I remembered the Chehov and Tolstoy portraits included in the Bunin memoir2 you kindly sent me and hoped that the other portraits would be on the same high level. Unfortunately they are not.

